{"text_id":127026,"tokens":["The"," Electoral"," College"," is"," a"," fundamental"," aspect"," of"," the"," United"," States"," presidential"," election"," process",","," and"," it"," should"," not"," be"," changed","."," Despite"," criticisms"," that"," it"," is"," outdated"," and"," und","em","ocratic",","," the"," Electoral"," College"," has"," several"," important"," benefits"," that"," make"," it"," an"," essential"," part"," of"," our"," political"," system",".","\n\n","First"," and"," foremost",","," the"," Electoral"," College"," helps"," to"," ensure"," a"," stable"," and"," orderly"," transfer"," of"," power"," from"," one"," administration"," to"," the"," next","."," By"," requiring"," a"," candidate"," to"," win"," a"," majority"," of"," electoral"," votes",","," instead"," of"," a"," simple"," plurality"," of"," the"," popular"," vote",","," the"," Electoral"," College"," helps"," to"," prevent"," election"," disputes"," and"," potential"," chaos","."," The"," founders"," of"," the"," United"," States"," recognized"," the"," dangers"," of"," a"," system"," where"," the"," president"," could"," be"," chosen"," by"," a"," narrow"," margin"," of"," popular"," votes",","," and"," they"," established"," the"," Electoral"," College"," to"," ensure"," a"," clear"," and"," decisive"," outcome"," in"," presidential"," elections",".","\n\n","Another"," benefit"," of"," the"," Electoral"," College"," is"," that"," it"," encourages"," presidential"," candidates"," to"," campaign"," in"," a"," broader"," range"," of"," states","."," In"," a"," purely"," popular"," vote"," system",","," candidates"," would"," likely"," focus"," their"," efforts"," on"," the"," most"," populous"," states",","," neglecting"," smaller"," states"," and"," those"," with"," fewer"," electoral"," votes","."," This"," would"," result"," in"," fewer"," presidential"," candidate"," appearances"," and"," less"," attention"," paid"," to"," the"," issues"," that"," matter"," most"," to"," voters"," in"," those"," states","."," The"," Electoral"," College",","," however",","," requires"," candidates"," to"," compete"," for"," votes"," in"," a"," diverse"," array"," of"," states",","," helping"," to"," ensure"," that"," the"," concerns"," of"," all"," Americans"," are"," taken"," into"," account"," during"," presidential"," campaigns",".","\n\n","Furthermore",","," the"," Electoral"," College"," serves"," as"," a"," safeguard"," against"," regional","ism"," and"," the"," potential"," tyranny"," of"," the"," majority","."," By"," requiring"," a"," candidate"," to"," win"," the"," support"," of"," a"," broad"," cross","-","section"," of"," the"," country",","," the"," Electoral"," College"," helps"," to"," ensure"," that"," no"," one"," region"," or"," group"," of"," states"," can"," dominate"," the"," political"," process","."," This"," is"," particularly"," important"," in"," a"," federal"," system"," like"," the"," United"," States",","," where"," different"," regions"," and"," states"," have"," diverse"," interests"," and"," priorities",".","\n\n","Critics"," argue"," that"," the"," Electoral"," College"," gives"," disproportion","ate"," influence"," to"," smaller"," states",","," but"," in"," reality",","," the"," system"," balances"," the"," interests"," of"," large"," and"," small"," states","."," The"," Electoral"," College"," allocation"," system",","," which"," is"," based"," on"," the"," number"," of"," representatives"," in"," Congress",","," ensures"," that"," every"," state"," has"," a"," voice"," in"," the"," presidential"," election","."," This"," balance"," helps"," to"," promote"," stability"," and"," national"," unity"," by"," giving"," all"," states"," a"," stake"," in"," the"," outcome"," of"," the"," election",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," the"," Electoral"," College"," should"," not"," be"," changed"," because"," it"," promotes"," a"," stable"," and"," orderly"," transfer"," of"," power",","," encourages"," candidates"," to"," campaign"," in"," a"," broader"," range"," of"," states",","," serves"," as"," a"," safeguard"," against"," regional","ism",","," and"," maintains"," a"," balance"," of"," power"," between"," large"," and"," small"," states","."," These"," benefits"," make"," the"," Electoral"," College"," an"," essential"," part"," of"," our"," political"," system",","," and"," any"," attempts"," to"," replace"," it"," with"," a"," popular"," vote"," system"," would"," likely"," lead"," to"," unintended"," consequences"," and"," potential"," instability",".","\n\n","Sources",":","\n\n","*"," Federal","ist"," No","."," ","6","8"," (","Alexander"," Hamilton",")","\n","*"," Why"," the"," Electoral"," College"," Is"," Too"," Important"," to"," Ignore"," -"," The"," Atlantic"," (","February"," ","2","0","1","6",")","\n","*"," The"," Electoral"," College",":"," A"," Shield"," Against"," Majority"," Tyran","ny"," -"," The"," Heritage"," Foundation"," (","August"," ","2","0","1","8",")","\n","*"," The"," Electoral"," College"," Provides"," Stability"," in"," the"," Presidential"," Selection"," Process"," -"," The"," Federal","ist"," Society"," (","February"," ","2","0","1","9",")","\n","*"," The"," Case"," for"," the"," Electoral"," College"," -"," National"," Affairs"," (","Summer"," ","2","0","1","9",")"],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}